    Setup

    Runs all proceedures to set up a valid iVXjs experience.

    public runSetup(): Promise source

    Runs a quick set up that will produce an iVXjs experience. It performs all set up tasks available in this order:

    1. Get data from a data processor.
    2. Validate the data.
    3. Add any other plugins for this experience.

    Return:

    Promise

    resolves when the set up is done.
